		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Start the game as Astarion.&#xD;&#xA;Recruit Gale.&#xD;&#xA;Bite him." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="19" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Astarion bit Gale in gameplay. Astarion got poisoned, a short dialog between Gale and Astarion. Several possible lines:&#xD;&#xA;1. Party doesn't know that Astarion is a vampire. Astarion shocked Gale's blood is like bile, Gale shocked Astarion is a vampire.&#xD;&#xA;2. Party knows Astarion is a vampire and he tried to bite Gale during a camp night. Gale mocks him a bit - &quot;you don't learn, do you?&quot;&#xD;&#xA;3. Party knows Astarion is a vampire, but he hasn't bitten Gale yet. Astarion is surprised by Gale's blood, Gale tells him think before biting other people." />
			<children>
